{"tid":1896094,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"罪成囚十年 桂民海  : 司法機關充分保障桂民海依法享有的各項訴訟權利","createTime":"2020-02-25T02:35:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T02:51:54.000Z","uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a5d58ac8664bb68e3302aa3ad9b5f21b3593976e","tid":1896094,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T02:35:59.000Z","msg":"在內地被拘留的銅鑼灣書店前東主桂民海，被寧波市中級人民法院，裁定「為境外非法提供情報」罪名成立，一審判處有期徒刑十年，剝奪政治權利五年。<br />\n<br />\n法院昨日公開宣判。根據公告，桂民海表示認罪服判不上訴，又說案件辦理過程中，司法機關充分保障桂民海依法享有的各項訴訟權利。部份社會群眾旁聽宣判。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1267332&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1267332%26csid%3D261_341&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpV3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=01e59206\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1267332&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"0f7a9ada80ee079647586ff1d3642290aee4abc8","tid":1896094,"uid":301952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T02:40:04.000Z","msg":"我萬珠莎華就最鍾意講道理架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a68ba6b2e988750ac710076bab461d4232892df","tid":1896094,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T02:43:43.000Z","msg":"psih"},{"pid":"ac97077d0890234499b6f2c4d25e714f08d899db","tid":1896094,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T02:51:54.000Z","msg":"push"}]}